  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Solution<Object>

    public class ObjectSolution
extends Object
implements Solution<Object>
    Solution used to wrap any type of decision variable.

    Notes:
    This class was created to load solution from files and assume that getVariable(int).toString() return the correct string to represent the value.
